    <p>If you are not on campus, we advise that you should visit your healthcare practitioner or primary physician as soon as possible and report your symptoms to them for evaluation.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>If you are already on campus and feeling ill, we advise you should visit your healthcare practitioner or primary physician as soon as possible and report your symptoms to them for evaluation.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>If it is a medical emergency, call 911. If you are ever in doubt of whether a situation is an emergency, you should call 911. It's better to be safe and let the dispatcher determine if you need emergency assistance. Otherwise, visit your healthcare practitioner or primary physician immediately.</p>
    





