                        <a id="accordion-1565284725626-last-week-i-was-with-a-friend-who-has-now-been-diagnosed-with-a-communicable-disease--what-should-i-do-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1565284725626-last-week-i-was-with-a-friend-who-has-now-been-diagnosed-with-a-communicable-disease--what-should-i-do-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1565284725626-last-week-i-was-with-a-friend-who-has-now-been-diagnosed-with-a-communicable-disease--what-should-i-do-" aria-expanded="false">
