<p>If you have any media requests about public health threats and/or communicable diseases at Ryerson, please contact Lindsey Craig, public affairs and communications specialist, at <a href="mailto:lindseyc@ryerson.ca">lindseyc@ryerson.ca</a>.&nbsp;</p> 
